data.eml:eml: INVESTIGATING THE MICROBIAL EUKARYOTIC COMMUNITIES IN THE SURFACE WATERS OF THE ARAFURA SEA AND CORAL SEA

WE INVESTIGATED THE DIVERSITY OF MICROBIAL EUKARYOTES IN THE SURFACE WATERS OF THE ARAFURA SEA, TORRES STRAIT AND CORAL SEA, USING FLOW CYTOMETRY AND HIGH-THROUGHPUT SEQUENCING OF THE V9 REGION OF THE 18S rRNA GENE.
